{"tid":769253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［蝻禍］排隊買JJ Concert飛 港男被蝻男斬","createTime":"2018-08-06T04:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T05:39:53.000Z","uid":38778,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c622d5b572a8c2cde2152961e418a63aa362bb2b","tid":769253,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:46:29.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180806/58528386\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180806%2F58528386&d=oOZMTXzW7vfu8itstuCjnSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=4cd05a80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180806%2F58528386&h=2ad8d5e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180806/58528386</a><br />\n<br />\n紅磡黃埔花園環海街通利琴行對開，早上6時許，26歲青年排隊輪候林俊傑(JJ)演唱會門票期間遇襲，遭兩名南亞裔男子持刀及木棍襲擊。事主閃避不及左手被斬傷，惡漢傷人後逃去無蹤，傷者自行乘的士到醫院求助。<br />\n<br />\n林俊傑，新加坡男歌手、詞曲創作者、音樂製作人，暱稱JJ，在台灣定居。「JJ 林俊傑香港演唱會2018」將於9月23日至25日共3場，在紅磡香港體育館演出，門票於本周三(8日)公開發售。據知，遇襲事主，於昨日下午3時半左右到來排隊。而現場也有其他人在排隊，但拒絕接受訪問。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ncls蝻畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9e6353cf21d339e6db3d70b3aa8b2d8a9fe9b2","tid":769253,"uid":38778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2520b524f6c45990592fc38721b6075e829545","tid":769253,"uid":66889,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"多謝張超雄"},{"pid":"3657008983bf63d927b7c0ce75f4cfccf57d2771","tid":769253,"uid":38778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:50:10.000Z","msg":"屌而家排隊買張飛都比人斬<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母南亞狗"},{"pid":"43da84f73e98476dc62d0a0e39cd63ac94ba40d3"